=== 拍攝 ===
拍攝預計於2010年春季於柏林展開<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1231717/KATIE-NICHOLL-How-strain-start-career-minded-Gwyneth-Paltrow-Chris-Martin-set-spend-time-apart.html How the strain may start to show as career-minded Gwyneth Paltrow and Chris Martin set to spend time apart] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1231717/KATIE-NICHOLL-How-strain-start-career-minded-Gwyneth-Paltrow-Chris-Martin-set-spend-time-apart.html |date=20201109025900 }} Daily Mail. 30 November 2009</ref><ref>[http://www.vancouversun.com/entertainment/serious+business+becoming+woman/2572626/story.html The serious business of becoming a woman]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Vancouver Sun. 16 February 2010</ref>。編劇告訴《創意劇本創作》，當最後導演開拍時，他實際上使用了舊版的劇本。「劇本在交給湯姆之前，我們可能已經寫過20個草稿。導演看回2008年的草稿，事實上，我們拍攝的是一個修訂過的早期版本。我替導演作了個很大程度的修改，但最終我們使用了僅略為修改過的原版。」

拍攝於2015年2月開始，那時[[埃迪·雷德梅尼|艾迪·瑞德曼]]已在劇組<ref>{{cite web |last=Smith |first=Ryan |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2973482/Eddie-Redmayne-begins-work-movie-Danish-Girl.html |title=Eddie Redmayne begins work on his movie The Danish Girl | Daily Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2015-09-06 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030000149/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2973482/Eddie-Redmayne-begins-work-movie-Danish-Girl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於[[新港_(哥本哈根)|新港 (哥本哈根)]]取景，那裡標誌性的濱水區看起來就像20世紀30年代的哥本哈根<ref>{{cite web|title=Filmstjerner genskaber 1930ernes København|url=http://underholdning.tv2.dk/underholdning/2015-03-30-se-billederne-filmstjerner-genskaber-1930ernes-koebenhavn|website=TV2.dk|language=da|accessdate=2016-02-23|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306101113/http://underholdning.tv2.dk/underholdning/2015-03-30-se-billederne-filmstjerner-genskaber-1930ernes-koebenhavn|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Filming of The Danish Girl in Copenhagen|url=http://www.thelocal.dk/galleries/4/filming-of-the-danish-girl-in-copenhagen/2|website=thelocal.dk|accessdate=2016-02-23|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033409/http://www.thelocal.dk/galleries/4/filming-of-the-danish-girl-in-copenhagen/2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref>{{cite web |last=Flint |first=Hanna |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3009135/PICTURE-EXCLUSIVE-Eddie-Redmayne-beaten-Danish-Girl-set.html |title=Eddie Redmayne is beaten as Einar Wegener on The Danish Girl set & No. 124; Daily Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2015-03-24 |accessdate=2015-09-06 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030000156/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3009135/PICTURE-EXCLUSIVE-Eddie-Redmayne-beaten-Danish-Girl-set.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dailymail.co.uk">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2973482/Eddie-Redmayne-begins-work-movie-Danish-Girl.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-09-02 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030000149/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2973482/Eddie-Redmayne-begins-work-movie-Danish-Girl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dailymail.co.uk"/>。拍攝地點設定為[[倫敦|倫敦]]工作室設立的[[丹麥|丹麥]]和[[巴黎|巴黎]]的房屋單位，以及額外於[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]及[[布魯塞爾-首都大區|布魯塞爾]]取景。電影製作於2015年4月12日殺青，花了44天於6個國家共186個場景拍攝<ref name="specs">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/eddie-redmayne-the-danish-girl-amy-berg-janis-little-girl-blue-specialty-preview-1201638291/|title=Eddie Redmayne Gets Dressed For ‘The Danish Girl’; Amy Berg Bows ‘Janis: Little Girl Blue’: Specialty Preview|author=Brian Brooks|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2015-11-25|accessdate=2015-11-29|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024131915/https://deadline.com/2015/11/eddie-redmayne-the-danish-girl-amy-berg-janis-little-girl-blue-specialty-preview-1201638291/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 後期製作 ==
電影的後期製作於2015年9月完成<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wearemoviegeeks.com/2015/11/eddie-redmayne-laverne-cox-at-special-screening-of-tom-hoopers-the-danish-girl/|title=Eddie Redmayne & Laverne Cox At Special Screening Of Tom Hooper’s THE DANISH GIRL|first=Michelle|last=McCue|date=2015-11-09|accessdate=2015-12-21|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004043116/http://www.wearemoviegeeks.com/2015/11/eddie-redmayne-laverne-cox-at-special-screening-of-tom-hoopers-the-danish-girl/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據作曲家[[亞歷山大·達士勒|亞歷山大·達士勒]]，後期製作的進度飛快，達士勒在電影剪接時寫曲，曲目錄製離電影於[[威尼斯電影節|威尼斯電影節]]上首映只有一星期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/artisans/news/danish-girl-alexandre-desplat-music-1201662338/|title=Alexandre Desplat on the Music Challenges & Rewards of ‘Danish Girl’|publisher=Variety.com|first=Tim|last=Gray|date=2015-12-15|accessdate=2015-12-21|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512091919/https://variety.com/2015/artisans/news/danish-girl-alexandre-desplat-music-1201662338/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

導演在一些電視訪談節目上透露電影的結局與小說及真實歷史不同，小說中格爾達與漢斯在一起，真實歷史中莉莉人生的最後歲月格爾達沒有和他相伴；他也不再強調漢斯那段故事的重要性，因為他不想格爾達與漢斯的愛可和格爾達與莉莉的感情相提並論。他想要一種模糊曖昧，寧可格爾達與漢斯的關係傾向一段外遇而不是友誼。因為對於他來說，格爾達和莉莉為彼此的畢生摯愛。他採用此走向的劇本版本來保護他們關係的重要性<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/tom-hooper-explains-why-he-cast-eddie-redmayne-as-the-danish-girl-20151125|title=Tom Hooper Explains Why He Cast Eddie Redmayne as 'The Danish Girl'|publisher=Variety.com|first=Kristy|last=Puchko|date=2015-11-25|accessdate=2016-02-03|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503172409/http://www.indiewire.com/article/tom-hooper-explains-why-he-cast-eddie-redmayne-as-the-danish-girl-20151125|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="After Ellen"/>。

在另一個訪問，女主角[[艾莉西亞·薇坎德|艾莉西亞·薇坎德]]透露，她有兩個跟Amber跳舞的場景從電影刪除，以及電影的初剪版超過兩小時長<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EEAedZFjRJo|title=The Danish Girl Deleted Scenes: Cast's Favourite|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube.com]]|first=MTV|last=International|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310095438/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EEAedZFjRJo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

